  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/9dfa84e9fa63bfdabaa64930076d9052.avif?t=1760051485\" width=800 height=1131 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restaurant Simulator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Concept:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the fast-paced world of Drive Thru Miami—a vibrant restaurant simulator where you become the ultimate drive-thru chef. Take orders, prepare drinks and meals, manage inventory, customize your shop, and grow your food empire in sunny Miami. Perfect for fans of cooking games, restaurant management, and simulation strategy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simulation of running and expanding a drive-thru shop where players take orders, prepare various beverages and foods, manage supplies, and serve customers efficiently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay Elements: <br><br>1. Order Taking: <br>- Receive and input customer orders for both beverages and foods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>2. Preparation:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Choose the correct cup size and shape for beverages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Prepare food items as requested.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>3. Customization: <br>- Customize your shop and prices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Payment System: <br>- Process payments using cash, credit cards, or mobile payments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Input amounts, provide correct change, and complete transactions accurately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5. Supply Management: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - Monitor inventory and restock supplies to keep the shop well-stocked.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Growth and Expansion: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - Improve and expand the shop by upgrading equipment, adding new menu items, and opening new locations. <br>- Invest profits wisely to enhance the shop's reputation and attract more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Objective: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Efficiently manage and grow the drive-thru, accurately fulfill orders, maintain adequate supplies, and build a positive reputation for your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game offers a dynamic and realistic experience of operating and expanding a drive-thru, managing a wide range of beverages and foods, handling diverse payment transactions, and ensuring a steady supply of goods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restaurant Simulator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Concept:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the fast-paced world of Drive Thru Miami—a vibrant restaurant simulator where you become the ultimate drive-thru chef. Take orders, prepare drinks and meals, manage inventory, customize your shop, and grow your food empire in sunny Miami. Perfect for fans of cooking games, restaurant management, and simulation strategy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simulation of running and expanding a drive-thru shop where players take orders, prepare various beverages and foods, manage supplies, and serve customers efficiently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay Elements: <br><br>1. Order Taking: <br>- Receive and input customer orders for both beverages and foods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>2. Preparation:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Choose the correct cup size and shape for beverages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Prepare food items as requested.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>3. Customization: <br>- Customize your shop and prices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Payment System: <br>- Process payments using cash, credit cards, or mobile payments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Input amounts, provide correct change, and complete transactions accurately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5. Supply Management: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - Monitor inventory and restock supplies to keep the shop well-stocked.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.poster.avif?t=1760051485\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.webm?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119780/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.mp4?t=1760051485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Growth and Expansion: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - Improve and expand the shop by upgrading equipment, adding new menu items, and opening new locations. <br>- Invest profits wisely to enhance the shop's reputation and attract more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Objective: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Efficiently manage and grow the drive-thru, accurately fulfill orders, maintain adequate supplies, and build a positive reputation for your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game offers a dynamic and realistic experience of operating and expanding a drive-thru, managing a wide range of beverages and foods, handling diverse payment transactions, and ensuring a steady supply of goods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
